responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "194C06664A52D40C8E0123A503827E9B", "Look around you. This is a beacon of commerce amidst a hostile realm. Nay! This is a beacon of hope courtesy of me, Lord Kivan Daragal. Let\'s pray to the Seven that we can keep the goblins at bay or we\'ll be back to square one.")
